COOKE

COOKE. No. 418P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 24, 2008. K. Edward Greene, Tobias S. Hampson, Raleigh, for Susan Cooke.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 11th day of September 2007 by Plaintiff to Withdraw Petition:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 24th day of January 2008."
